      <title>拜登的发电厂计划将具有更大的碳减排范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/biden-s-power-plant-pollution-curbs-set-to-cut-more-emissions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国电力需求不断攀升，拜登政府遏制发电厂污染的计划预计将比最初预期大幅减少温室气体排放。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/biden-s-power-plant-pollution-curbs-set-to-cut-more-emissions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 18:57:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡塔尔将召开会议讨论乌克兰结束战争的提议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/qatar-will-host-meeting-to-discuss-ukrainian-proposal-to-end-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，来自世界各地的国家安全顾问和高级官员将于本周末在多哈举行会议，讨论就乌克兰与俄罗斯和解的条件举行峰会的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/qatar-will-host-meeting-to-discuss-ukrainian-proposal-to-end-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 18:54:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着移民成本稳定，纽约市市长恢复了对警察的资助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/nyc-mayor-restores-funding-for-police-as-migrant-costs-stabilize</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯 (Eric Adams) 推翻了削减警察部门和幼儿教育的提议，因为该市能够降低移民护理成本，而且税收收入好于预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/nyc-mayor-restores-funding-for-police-as-migrant-costs-stabilize</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 18:49:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>部长称拜登“忠实地”追随特朗普在古巴问题上的脚步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/biden-faithfully-follows-trump-s-steps-on-cuba-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[外交部副部长卡洛斯·费尔南德斯·德科西奥表示，在美古关系问题上，乔·拜登总统一直“忠实地”追随其前任的脚步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/biden-faithfully-follows-trump-s-steps-on-cuba-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 18:45:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登禁止在新联邦建筑中使用化石燃料</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/gas-use-banned-in-new-federal-buildings-under-biden-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据拜登政府的一项规定，从 2030 年开始，新的联邦建筑将禁止使用化石燃料，天然气行业为此奋斗了十多年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/gas-use-banned-in-new-federal-buildings-under-biden-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 18:01:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙首相桑切斯表示他正在考虑辞去总理职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/spain-s-sanchez-says-he-s-considering-quitting-as-premier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯表示，由于他和妻子最近几周遭遇袭击，他正在考虑辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/spain-s-sanchez-says-he-s-considering-quitting-as-premier</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 17:32:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯资产扣押法引发耶伦赞扬，美元担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/russia-asset-seizure-law-spurs-yellen-praise-angst-over-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会周二通过授权总统乔·拜登扣押俄罗斯美元资产以援助乌克兰的新权力，加剧了有关外国对美国国债需求和使用美元的潜在后果的争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/russia-asset-seizure-law-spurs-yellen-praise-angst-over-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:24:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求佐治亚州法官撤销选举案中的两项罪名</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/trump-asks-georgia-judge-to-toss-two-counts-in-election-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普要求法官撤销佐治亚州选举舞弊案中的两项罪名，称当地富尔顿县地方检察官法尼·威利斯不能指控他在联邦法院提交虚假文件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/trump-asks-georgia-judge-to-toss-two-counts-in-election-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:20:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着以色列与哈马斯之间的紧张局势蔓延，哈佛大学的抗议活动不断加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/protest-deadline-passes-at-columbia-as-talks-fail-to-end-impasse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈佛大学的学生就以色列与哈马斯冲突升级了校园抗议活动，效仿哥伦比亚大学、耶鲁大学和纽约大学爆发的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/protest-deadline-passes-at-columbia-as-talks-fail-to-end-impasse</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 07:14:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
